-- SMS Plans to Acquire Arcelor’s Paul Wurth Stake, Boersen Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-06-05T17:47:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-05/sms-plans-to-acquire-arcelor-s-paul-wurth-stake-boersen-says.html
SMS Group plans to acquire
 ArcelorMittal (MT) ’s 48 percent stake in Paul Wurth,  Boersen-Zeitung 
reported in a preview of an article that will be published
tomorrow, citing SMS Chief Executive Officer Heinrich Weiss.  SMS is currently in talks with the state of Luxembourg,
which owns a majority of Paul Wurth, regarding approval of the
planned acquisition, the newspaper said, citing Weiss.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
